msgid ""
"A take is a recording of a verse or chunk; a verse/chunk can have "
"multiple takes. Immediately after recording a take, the program "
"automatically advances to the Edit screen. You can also navigate to the "
"Edit screen for a completed take by tapping the Waveform icon on the "
"`Take bar`_ of the Verse or Chunk list."
